Algorithm:
1)Start
2)Read first text
3)Read second text
4)Convert both texts into TF-IDF vectors
5)Calculate cosine similarity between vectors
6)Convert similarity score into percentage
7)Display result
8)Stop

Flowchart:
Start
  ↓
Input Text 1 & Text 2
  ↓
TF-IDF Vectorization
  ↓
Cosine Similarity Calculation
  ↓
Convert to Percentage
  ↓
Display Similarity
  ↓
End
